#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Introdución"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; is a small program to practice calculating with fractions and "
"percentages. Six different exercises are offered as well as a learning mode."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; é un programiña para practicar o cálculo con fraccións e "
"porcentaxes. Ofrece seis tipos distintos de exercicio con este propósito, "
"así como un modo de aprendizaxe."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:72
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Arithmetic - in this exercise you have to solve a given fraction task. "
#| "You have to enter the numerator and the denominator. This is the main "
#| "exercise."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Arithmetic</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to solve a given "
"fraction task. You have to enter the numerator and the denominator. This is "
"the main exercise."
msgstr ""
"Aritmética - neste exercicio hai que resulver un problema cunha fracción "
"dada. Hai que inserir o numerador e o denominador. Este é o tipo principal "
"de exercicio."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:76
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Comparison - in this exercise you have to compare the size of 2 given "
#| "fractions, using the symbols <guibutton>&gt;</guibutton>, <guibutton>&lt;"
#| "</guibutton> or <guibutton>=</guibutton>."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Comparison</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to compare the "
"size of 2 given fractions, using the symbols <guibutton>&gt;</guibutton>, "
"<guibutton>&lt;</guibutton> or <guibutton>=</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Comparación - neste exercicio hai que comparar o tamaño de dúas fraccións "
"dadas empregando os símbolos <guibutton>&gt;</guibutton>, <guibutton>&lt;</"
"guibutton> e <guibutton>=</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:81
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Conversion - in this exercise you have to convert a given number into a "
#| "fraction."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Conversion</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to convert a "
"given number into a fraction."
msgstr ""
"Conversión - nestes exercicios hai que converter un número dado nunha "
"fracción."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Mixed Numbers - in this exercise you have to convert a mixed number into "
#| "an improper fraction (ratio) and vice versa."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Mixed Numbers</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to convert a "
"mixed number into an improper fraction (ratio) and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Números mixtos - neste exercicio hai que converter un número mixo a unha "
"fracción impropia e viceversa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:89
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Factorization - in this exercise you have to factorize a given number "
#| "into its prime factors."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Factorization</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to factorize "
"a given number into its prime factors."
msgstr ""
"Factorización - neste exercicio hai que descompor un número dado nos seus "
"factores primos."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Percentage - in this exercise you have to calculate percentages."
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Percentage</guilabel> - in this exercise you have to calculate "
"percentages."
msgstr "Porcentaxe - neste exercicio hai que calcular porcentaxes."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In each different exercise &kbruch; will generate a task and the user has to "
"solve it. The program checks the input and gives a feedback about it."
msgstr ""
"En todos os tipos de exercicios &kbruch; xera un problema e o usuario tenque "
"resolvelo. O programa comproba a entrada do usuario e dá unha resposta sobre "
"ela."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; counts how many tasks were solved at all and how many tasks were "
"solved correctly. The statistics are shown to the user."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; leva a conta do número de problemas que foron resoltos e dos que o "
"foron correctamente. Amósalle as estatísticas ao usuario."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:109
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kbruch; is very compact and focuses on the core idea of a task generator. "
"An online help system provides context-sensitive help for the different "
"situations."
msgstr ""
"&kbruch; é moi compacto e focalízase na idea dun xerador de tarefas. O "
"sistema de axuda con conexión fornece axuda sensíbel ao contexto para as "
"distintas situacións."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using &kbruch;"
msgstr "Uso de &kbruch;"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choosing the mode: learning or exercises"
msgstr "Escolla do modo: aprendizaxe ou exercicios"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:123
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start &kbruch;, it offers you two modes: <guilabel>Exercise</"
"guilabel> which is the training mode and <guilabel>Learning</guilabel> where "
"you can understand fractions. Clicking one of the pictures will enter the "
"chosen mode. Here is a screenshot of &kbruch;'s mode choices:"
msgstr ""
"Ao iniciar &kbruch; este ofrece dous modos: <guilabel>Exercicio</guilabel>, "
"que é o modo de adestramento, e <guilabel>Aprendizaxe</guilabel>, no que se "
"poden comprender as fraccións. Ao premer unha das imaxes éntrase no modo "
"escollido. Velaquí unha pantalla coas escollas de modo de &kbruch;:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&kbruch; mode choices</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Escollas de modo de &kbruch;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&kbruch; mode choices</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Escollas de modo de &kbruch;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid "Click one of the picture to choose the mode."
msgstr "Preme unha das imaxes para escolleres o modo."

